resources.string: This app needs to be able to access your location so that it can calculate the distance between locations. FINE location access allows this app to use location information provided by GPS and WiFi radios. Without these permissions this app will not work.

This app needs to be able to access your location so that it can calculate the distance between locations. COARSE location access allows this app to use location information provided by Cellular radio towers. Without these permissions this app will not work.
Please grant location permissions for this app.
